{"type":"message","id":"461ed983","parentId":"07e17e9c","timestamp":"2026-03-17T00:51:28.466Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:17","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Config warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.feishu: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected; later plugin may be overridden (C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\extensions\\feishu\\index.ts)\n|\no  Config warnings --------------------------------------------------------+\n|                                                                          |\n|  - plugins.entries.feishu: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected;  |\n|    later plugin may be overridden                                        |\n|    (C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\extensions\\feishu\\index.ts)                   |\n|                                                                          |\n+--------------------------------------------------------------------------+\nSkills (32/76 ready)\n+-----------+--------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------+\n| Status    | Skill                          | Description                                        | Source             |\n+-----------+--------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------+\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 feishu-doc                  | Feishu document read/write operations. Activate    | openclaw-extra     |\n|           |                                | when user mentions Feishu docs, cloud docs, or     |                    |\n|           |                                | docx links.                                        |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 feishu-drive                | Feishu cloud storage file management. Activate     | openclaw-extra     |\n|           |                                | when user mentions cloud space, folders, drive.    |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 feishu-perm                 | Feishu permission mana