{"type":"message","id":"43462c52","parentId":"76de1c1f","timestamp":"2026-03-17T01:54:58.591Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"机器人搜不到的问题。让我检查一下飞书插件的配置情况。根据之前的查看，飞书插件确实已经加载了。问题可能在于：\n\n1. 应用未在飞书管理后台发布\n2. 应用未开启机器人能力\n3. 应用未上架到飞书应用市场\n\n让我给主人提供一个排查方案。主人，搜索不到机器人的问题通常是因为**应用未在飞书管理后台发布**或者**未开启机器人能力**。\n\n让我帮您检查配置并提供解决方案：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:37","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw config list 2>&1 | findstr -i \"feishu\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:38","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/extensions/feishu/package.json"}},{"type":"thinking","thinking":"或","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"length","timestamp":1773712286785}}
