{"type":"message","id":"55318097","parentId":"2439c6ef","timestamp":"2026-03-17T13:16:21.404Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking why I didn't respond to their previous message about searching for papers by \"兰文升\" from Xi'an University of Electronic Science and Technology. \n\nLooking at the conversation history, I actually did respond with a detailed message explaining that I tried multiple search methods but couldn't find any papers. The user might not have received the message or there was a delay.\n\nI should acknowledge that I did respond and provide the information again to ensure they receive it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，我回了的！🙋‍♂️ 让我再给您发一遍搜索结果：\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 西安电子科技大学 兰文升 论文搜索结果\n\n我使用了多种方法搜索，但**暂未找到相关论文记录**：\n\n### 已尝试的搜索方式：\n1. **Google Scholar**（谷歌学术）\n2. **中国知网（CNKI）**\n3. **西安电子科技大学官网**（师资队伍页面）\n4. **通用搜索引擎**（百度/Google）\n\n### 可能原因：\n1. **非学术岗位** - 可能从事行政/技术/教学岗位，不以发论文为主\n2. **论文数量少** - 可能论文较少或未被搜索引擎收录\n3. **姓名差异** - 可能有不同的姓名拼写方式\n4. **已离校** - 人员可能已离校或信息未公开\n\n### 建议：\n- 提供更多线索（如：具体院系、研究方向、大致时间段）\n- 直接联系西安电子科技大学相关院系查询\n- 尝试万方/维普等其他学术数据库\n\n---\n\n您收到这条消息了吗？如果还是看不到，可能是飞书消息推送有延迟，我再给您重发一次！📨"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773753286574}}
